{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[BEEP] [SIDE CONVERSATION]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were many rumors about the-- what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my, my mother and I decided that we should hide some of our valuables.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother hid some of our-- some of her jewelry in, in the basement under the coal-- she dug.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also carried down into the basement my father's set of the Talmud, which we were able to recover after the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also hid some, some of the stuff that we thought were very important in our lives-- such as soap-- in a certain a place in the bathroom, which we could later recover.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "News came out every day, what we can do and what we cannot do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then one day, it was announced that we will be taken somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they called us to line up outside the court yard, the whole building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they Hungarian gendarmes came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they searched us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They searched our bodies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The-- they actually searched our bodies manually to see if we were hiding anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they told us to line up outside the gate of our building, and take with us whatever we could carry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know that because I was 15, and I was so, so-- such a idealist, I did not think of anything that could save my life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I brought with me things that were important in my life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I brought with me pictures, and my diary, and I had a notebook where I put down important quotations from my readings that I accumulated throughout my life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in the last minute, my mother said, well where is your sweater?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I stuck in a sweater there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
